Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ following \First Look-Your updates are overdue\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'First Look-Your updates are overdue' occurs

Name: Percentage of manuscripts that reach \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ stage out of all manuscripts
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all cases where '' does not happen

Name: Number of times \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ is the final activity before \Manuscript Export Succeeded\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' occurs

Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ preceded by \First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ occurrences out of all activities in the review process
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all cases where '' does not happen

Name: Ratio of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ over \SW-AE Assign Reviewers\ in the manuscript review process
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Number of manuscripts that proceed to \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ within 1 month of \First Look-Please submit updates\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'First Look-Please submit updates' occurs

Name: Percentage of manuscripts that bypass \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ after \First Look-Your updates are due in one week\
Metric: the average of the function base > 0 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` != 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'First Look-Your updates are due in one week'

Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ in relation to total number of manuscripts submitted
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity '' does not occur

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ followed by \Manuscript Export Succeeded\ in the review process
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'
